# Tailwind CSS — Dark UI Patterns (Soulspedia)

## Core Rules
- Tailwind CSS v4 with PostCSS. Some v3 utilities may not exist — verify before using.
- CSS custom properties in `app/globals.css` take priority over hardcoded values.
- Never use arbitrary color values when a token exists.
- `overflow-x: clip` on `html` — never override.

---

## Design Tokens

### Colors
```
Background base:   #050505      → bg-[#050505]       Never bg-black
Accent gold:       amber-100/90 → text-amber-100/90
Accent bone:       white/82     → text-white/82
Lore text:         #e0e0d8      → text-[#e0e0d8]
Border subtle:     white/5      → border-white/5
Border visible:    white/15     → border-white/15
Border emphasis:   white/25     → border-white/25
```
Borders are **always semi-transparent**. No opaque borders ever.

### Typography
```
font-optimus → OptimusPrinceps. Always uppercase. tracking-[0.06em] minimum.
font-lore    → EB Garamond. tracking-tight. text-base minimum.
```

### Layout utilities
```
.page-shell    → max-w-[80rem] mx-auto px-[var(--page-margin-x)]
.page-gutter-x → px-[var(--page-margin-x)]  (no max-width)
```
Never hardcode horizontal margins. Always use `.page-shell` or `--page-margin-x`.

---

## Recurring Effect Classes

### Text glows
```tsx
// Dark atmospheric glow (default state)
"[text-shadow:0_0_14px_rgba(0,0,0,0.82),0_0_42px_rgba(75,42,12,0.38),0_0_88px_rgba(42,22,8,0.22)]"

// Gold hover glow
"hover:[text-shadow:0_0_14px_rgba(252,211,77,0.55),0_0_28px_rgba(251,146,60,0.42),0_0_48px_rgba(234,88,12,0.22)]"
```

### Gradient overlays
```tsx
// Section top fade
"bg-gradient-to-b from-black/90 via-black/55 to-transparent"

// Section bottom fade
"bg-gradient-to-t from-black/90 via-black/40 to-transparent"

// Ambient radial glow
"bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_70%_50%,rgba(255,80,0,0.1)_0%,rgba(0,0,0,0.9)_70%)]"

// Image vignette
"bg-[radial-gradient(ellipse_at_center,transparent_30%,rgba(0,0,0,0.85)_100%)]"
```

### Cards and containers
```tsx
// Base card
"relative border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.02] backdrop-blur-sm"

// Hover state
"transition-colors duration-700 hover:border-white/15 hover:bg-white/[0.04]"

// Separator line
"h-px w-full bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-white/10 to-transparent"
```

