## Responsive Patterns

```tsx
// Grid: 1 col → 2 → 3 → 4
"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 xl:grid-cols-4 gap-6"

// Typography scaling
"text-sm md:text-base lg:text-lg"

// Full bleed mobile, contained desktop
"w-full lg:max-w-[80rem] lg:mx-auto"
```

