## Advanced Patterns

### group-hover for card reveals
```tsx
<div className="group relative overflow-hidden">
  <Image className="transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-105" ... />
  <div className="absolute inset-0 opacity-0 transition-opacity duration-500 group-hover:opacity-100">
    <span className="font-optimus uppercase tracking-[0.06em] text-amber-100/90">{name}</span>
  </div>
</div>
```

### peer for form states
```tsx
<input className="peer bg-transparent border-b border-white/10 focus:border-amber-100/50 outline-none transition-colors duration-500" />
<label className="peer-focus:text-amber-100/70 transition-colors duration-300">Email</label>
```

### Arbitrary CSS properties (Tailwind v4)
```tsx
"[text-shadow:...]"            // custom shadow
"[writing-mode:vertical-rl]"   // vertical text
```

---

## ❌ Anti-Patterns
- `bg-black` → use `bg-[#050505]`
- Hardcoded `px-4 mx-auto max-w-7xl` → use `.page-shell`
- `border-white` or `border-gray-700` → always opacity variants
- `font-sans` or `font-serif` → use `font-optimus` or `font-lore`
- `transition` without duration → always `transition-colors duration-500`
- `text-white` for body text → use `text-[#e0e0d8]` or `text-white/82`
- `rounded-xl` or `rounded-2xl` → max `rounded-sm`, prefer `rounded-none`
- `shadow-lg` → use custom rgba text-shadow or drop-shadow
